\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">pid</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__2\">I4</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__4\">Uniface Router's process ID</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">host</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__2\">C256</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__3\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__4\">Uniface Router's host and IP address</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">connet</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__2\">C3</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__3\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__4\">Connection network to Uniface Router\n                  (e.g.<code class=\"ph codeph\">tcp</code>)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">conaddr</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__2\">C8</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__3\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__4\">Connection address on Uniface Router (e.g. the port\n                number)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">lisnet1</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__2\">C3</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__3\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__4\">Listen network to Uniface Router (e.g.\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">TCP</code>)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">lisaddr1</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__2\">C8</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__3\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__4\">Listen address on Uniface Router (e.g. the port\n                number)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">lisnet2</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__2\">C3</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__3\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__4\">Listen network to Uniface Router (e.g.\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">TCP</code>)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">lisaddr2</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__2\">C8</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__3\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__4\">Listen address on Uniface Router (e.g. the port\n                number)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">lisnet3</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__2\">C3</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__3\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__4\">Listen network to Uniface Router (e.g.\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">TCP</code>)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">lisaddr3</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__2\">C8</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__3\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__4\">Listen address on Uniface Router (e.g. the port\n                number)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">startstamp</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__2\">E5</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__3\">Datetime</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgs1665703195669__table_x5p_nvk_gwb__entry__4\">Uniface Router started at dd-mmm-yyyy hh:mm:ss</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xgs1665703195669__section_qn2_pvk_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d550845e325\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">If successful, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span> is set to zero. Otherwise, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qln1665702528769.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qln1665702528769.html#qln1665702528769__section_fbt_4d2_gwb\">Return Codes</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xgs1665703195669__section_atn_rvk_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d550845e341\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Allowed in all Uniface component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xgs1665703195669__section_xfk_svk_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d550845e350\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The <span class=\"keyword apiname\">GET_UROUTER</span> operation gets static information about the Uniface\n        Router.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533721\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533721\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "GET_UROUTER Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 22, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Get static information about the Uniface Router. operation GET_UROUTER params entity UROUTERS.UROUTMON : OUT endparams Parameters UROUTERS.UROUTMON—single occurrence of entity UROUTERS.UROUTMON containing static information about the Uniface Router. Table 1. UROUTERS.UROUTMON entity Fieldname Packing Code/ Data Type Description pid I4 Numeric Uniface Router's process ID host C256 String Uniface Router's host and IP address connet C3 String Connection network to Uniface Router (e.g. tcp ) conaddr C8 String Connection address on Uniface Router (e.g. the port number) lisnet1 C3 String Listen network to Uniface Router (e.g. TCP ) lisaddr1 C8 String Listen address on Uniface Router (e.g. the port number) lisnet2 C3 String Listen network to Uniface Router (e.g. TCP ) lisaddr2 C8 String Listen address on Uniface Router (e.g. the port number) lisnet3 C3 String Listen network to Uniface Router (e.g. TCP ) lisaddr3 C8 String Listen address on Uniface Router (e.g. the port number) startstamp E5 Datetime Uniface Router started at dd-mmm-yyyy hh:mm:ss Return Values If successful, $status is set to zero. Otherwise, see Return Codes . Use Allowed in all Uniface component types. Description The GET_UROUTER operation gets static information about the Uniface Router. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}